{"tid":1606172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日冇一個手足俾人拉既戰術！","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:37:45.000Z","uid":213352,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a114bace39b9ffda7735520063317e63efd3cc4f","tid":1606172,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係班狗衝出黎捉人果陣唔好跑走</span><br />\n<br />\n其實都講到厭 但過左3個月 希望大家聽日進化到<br />\n可以咁做<br />\n<br />\n1.有盾既企最前（唔洗驚 後面有一大班人頂住）<br />\n2.盾陣後面可以扔野 施展魔法 阻住d狗攻擊盾陣<br />\n（放心聽日會有好多火同水魔法）<br />\n3. 再後排就可以不斷扔雜物<br />\n<br />\n咁樣我地就可以慢慢開始推進 <br />\n一二，一二 做口號 一聽到口號就可以慢慢向前<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以應承我 就算唔敢<br />\n都唔好扔低最前線既勇武 佢地企最前 一走就企最後<br />\n走唔切架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日 祝大家旗開得勝！"},{"pid":"abbfed084d6c64b7f1efb165194583d39ac91571","tid":1606172,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"91aa0943ad04236a3c9e48f23b57032831670a63","tid":1606172,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"578e9292b5b8f2f0ff6976290b915f44fe04863e","tid":1606172,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"十一特別版，習總連儂地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606161</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"850589f676594bb4c06d7c719ddc2c4b44a74c3b","tid":1606172,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:25:20.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"60f167a94b58172c56b45ad6078fcfd8e1019fc4","tid":1606172,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38d7de0761ebc7b072a8456b813ecb5d0ae21d9c","tid":1606172,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid